msgstr "Componente `Foo`"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/testing-components.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`Foo` is an `@ApplicationScoped` CDI bean."
msgstr "`Foo` é um bean CDI `com escopo @ApplicationScoped` ."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/testing-components.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`Foo` depends on `Charlie` which declares a method `ping()`."
msgstr "`Foo` depende de `Charlie` , que declara um método `chamado ping()` ."

